{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tutorial-js","path":"/zh/tutorial/Layout/DrawingObjects/Textgroup/","webpackCompilationHash":"b56fc1f276773fcd7503","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>“ <strong>对象操作</strong> ”选项卡上的“ <strong>文本</strong> ”按钮，用来在布局窗口中绘制文本对象。</p>\n<p>文本对象绘制  </p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>按钮</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n<th>功能及操作方法</th>\n<th>示意图</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b471cc76a0e4a47cc17b94c23a3ce5c6/cbd68/textButton.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 32px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"textButton\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b471cc76a0e4a47cc17b94c23a3ce5c6/cbd68/textButton.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b471cc76a0e4a47cc17b94c23a3ce5c6/cbd68/textButton.png 32w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 32px) 100vw, 32px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </td>\n<td>文本</td>\n<td>单击“文本”按钮，出现普通文本光标；在布局窗口中需要添加文本的位置单击鼠标左键，显示闪烁的光标；输入文本。输入文本时，文本在闪烁的光标处显示；单击</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Enter 键可另起一行。</td>\n<td>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/44387cad8a4dd4498537b9bb7caafc64/6d450/drawText.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 228px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 43.421052631578945%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"drawText\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/44387cad8a4dd4498537b9bb7caafc64/6d450/drawText.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/44387cad8a4dd4498537b9bb7caafc64/6a467/drawText.png 210w,\n/static/44387cad8a4dd4498537b9bb7caafc64/6d450/drawText.png 228w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 228px) 100vw, 228px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6b48fb2fed60ba154def47a52593b697/cbd68/alongLineTextButton.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 32px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"alongLineTextButton\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/6b48fb2fed60ba154def47a52593b697/cbd68/alongLineTextButton.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6b48fb2fed60ba154def47a52593b697/cbd68/alongLineTextButton.png 32w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 32px) 100vw, 32px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </td>\n<td>沿线标注</td>\n<td>沿着某一条曲线创建文本。单击“文本”按钮的下拉按钮，在弹出的下拉菜单中选择“沿线标注”，出现沿线文本光标!；在布局窗口中创建沿线文本的位置，单击鼠标左键，确定沿线文本的起始点，然后按照绘制曲线的方式绘制文本的沿线路径；沿线路径绘制完后，单击鼠标右键，弹出“沿线注记”对话框；在编辑框中输入沿线文本内容。单击“确定”按钮，完成绘制沿线文本操作。</td>\n<td>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9fa74507870e9ad313999ce27327e9f7/6d450/drawAlongLintText.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 228px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.15789473684211%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"drawAlongLintText\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/9fa74507870e9ad313999ce27327e9f7/6d450/drawAlongLintText.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9fa74507870e9ad313999ce27327e9f7/6a467/drawAlongLintText.png 210w,\n/static/9fa74507870e9ad313999ce27327e9f7/6d450/drawAlongLintText.png 228w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 228px) 100vw, 228px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"备注\"><a href=\"#%E5%A4%87%E6%B3%A8\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><img src=\"/read-56e09d9020b6fe36d2da63ae2fd275c5.gif\">备注</h3>\n<p>结束文本绘制有以下两种方式：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-text\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">* 在布局窗口中任意非文本框所在区域单击鼠标右键。\n* 再次单击“ **对象操作** ”选项卡“ **文本** ”组对应文本对象绘制的按钮。</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"绘制文本对象","next":null,"prev":null},"fields":{"path":"content\\tutorial\\Layout\\DrawingObjects\\Textgroup.zh.md","slug":"/zh/tutorial/Layout/DrawingObjects/Textgroup/","langKey":"zh"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/zh/tutorial/Layout/DrawingObjects/Textgroup/"}}}